name: WhereInTheWorldQuiz
0:
”Alexa, start Where World Quiz”
”Alexa, play Where World Quiz”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: where world quiz
des:
Test your knowledge of the World with "where in the world..." questions.

Where In The World Quiz asks you questions about famous food, places, festivals, landmarks of the world and more.

Answer 10 "where in the world..." questions to put your world GK to the test!

To start, just say "Alexa, launch Where World Quiz" or "Alexa, open Where World Quiz" to start the game".

You can stop the game anytime by saying "Alexa, stop"
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
